4
00:00:36,302 --> 00:00:37,782
<font color="#804040">CATHY</font>:
People use the color yellow...

5
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:40,040
To symbolize hope.

6
00:00:41,441 --> 00:00:43,250
Yellow...

7
00:00:43,309 --> 00:00:46,449
Like the sun
we rarely saw.

8
00:00:47,347 --> 00:00:49,554
When I was very young,
I thought life would be...

9
00:00:49,616 --> 00:00:53,325
Like one long and perfect
summer day.

10
00:00:53,386 --> 00:00:56,629
After all,
it started out that way.

11
00:00:59,526 --> 00:01:01,096
We were
four beautiful children...

12
00:01:01,161 --> 00:01:03,732
With blond hair
and porcelain skin.

13
00:01:06,199 --> 00:01:08,645
People said we looked like
those fancy dresden dolls...

14
00:01:08,701 --> 00:01:11,272
That grace shelves
and mantels.

15
00:01:11,337 --> 00:01:13,647
Only we weren't just admired.

16
00:01:13,706 --> 00:01:15,413
We were really loved.

17
00:01:19,646 --> 00:01:21,648
But that was before.

18
00:01:25,285 --> 00:01:28,459
"Life is full of surprises,"
my mother used to say.

19
00:01:29,823 --> 00:01:36,263
And greed and fear and shame,
as I soon learned.

20
00:01:38,431 --> 00:01:40,138
And hopelessness.

21
